{
  "title": "Cheat—— 给Linux初学者和管理员一个终极命令行\"备忘单\"",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当你不确定你所运行的命令，尤其是那些使用了许多选项的复杂命令时，你会怎么做？在这种情况下，我们使用man pages来获取帮助。还有一些其它的选择可能包括像‘<strong>help</strong>’，‘<strong>whereis</strong>’和‘<strong>whatis</strong>’这样的命令。但是所有的这些既有优点，也有缺点。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"quiver-image-url/ABDF4A36C7B1AE7E33BF53E59C65B523.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">当我们浏览<strong>man pages</strong>来查看选项和帮助的时候，里面的描述实在太冗长了，我们无法在短的时间里理解它的意思。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ce202326bd23b7839db919896d3548dc91ccc992/687474703a2f2f7777772e7465636d696e742e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031342f30372f4c696e75782d4d616e2d50616765732e6a706567\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0); transition: all 0.5s ease; text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Linux Man Pages\" data-canonical-src=\"http://s3.51cto.com/wyfs02/M00/49/22/wKioL1QPxhzRC-NXAAET8TLwLZs301.jpg-wh_600x-s_2369830004.jpg\" src=\"quiver-image-url/DCAFEE512EE62E251E96DBBF0D35D13A.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Linux Man Pages</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">同样，‘<strong>help</strong>’命令可能也不会给你期待的答案。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/96250682158db1bb3c9889531d4f8589e109c1fd/687474703a2f2f7777772e7465636d696e742e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031342f30372f68656c702d636f6d6d616e642e6a706567\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0); transition: all 0.5s ease; text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Help Command\" data-canonical-src=\"http://s4.51cto.com/wyfs02/M02/49/22/wKioL1QPxh2SxtKfAAHIIorsk24237.jpg-wh_600x-s_2198567156.jpg\" src=\"quiver-image-url/F65E014EBCC16BDF9E27C26C03D9C08A.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Help Command</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">‘<strong>whereis</strong>’命令几乎不给你任何信息，除了安装二进制文件的位置（有些时候可能是重要的）</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/f94b1fe991d7b95fd99a505c53baebe955ea71ad/687474703a2f2f7777772e7465636d696e742e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031342f30372f776865726569732d636f6d6d616e642e6a706567\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0); transition: all 0.5s ease; text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Whereis Command\" data-canonical-src=\"http://s7.51cto.com/wyfs02/M00/49/20/wKiom1QPxhCiVtBaAACBcnnUbjg779.jpg-wh_600x-s_3496153301.jpg\" src=\"quiver-image-url/932FFB173862E0C92BFEBF7777294FEF.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Whereis Command</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">‘<strong>whatis</strong>’命令给出一套很严格的答案，它除了说出所查询命令的作用，并没有什么太大帮助。而且，它从来不说明可用的选项。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d1f2b2d8a830108b1d8c38650649b6d2fbc4b1c0/687474703a2f2f7777772e7465636d696e742e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031342f30372f7768617469732d636f6d6d616e642e6a706567\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0); transition: all 0.5s ease; text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Whatis Command\" data-canonical-src=\"http://s6.51cto.com/wyfs02/M02/49/21/wKiom1QPxhCCrIomAACGLma6WsY298.jpg-wh_600x-s_360582073.jpg\" src=\"quiver-image-url/FC321B43CA0BACFF73B30C7B5EC15A6F.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Whatis Command</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">直到在困难中解决问题前，我们已经使用了以上全部选项，但是现在来了一个交互式的备忘录应用程序‘<strong>cheat</strong>’，它将在其余的命令中脱颖而出。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>什么是cheat?</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>cheat</strong>是在GNU通用公共许可证下，为Linux命令行用户发行的交互式备忘单应用程序。它提供显示Linux命令使用案例，包括该命令所有的选项和简短但尚可理解的功能。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7b4f156caaa898c7c9c9655143773f7fbd747a61/687474703a2f2f7777772e7465636d696e742e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031342f30372f63686561742d73686565742e6a706567\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0); transition: all 0.5s ease; text-decoration: none;\"><img alt=\"Cheat: Provides Easy Command Options\" data-canonical-src=\"http://s5.51cto.com/wyfs02/M01/49/22/wKioL1QPxh7DTZpkAAEMCMCd9UU783.jpg-wh_600x-s_494611290.jpg\" src=\"quiver-image-url/B3C02B44B3D853CD66B4DBF20060BD67.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\" width=\"876\" height=\"608\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Cheat：提供简单命令选项</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>在Linux系统中安装‘Cheat’</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">‘<strong>Cheat</strong>’有两个主要的依赖——‘<strong>python</strong>’ 和 ‘<strong>pip</strong>’，在安装‘<strong>cheat</strong>’之前，确保你的系统安装了python和pip。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Install Python</strong></p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1px !important;\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># apt-get install Python (基于Debian的系统)</span></li><li class=\"L1\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># yum install python (基于小红帽的系统)</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">Install Pip</p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1px !important;\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># apt-get install python-pip (基于Debian的系统)</span></li><li class=\"L1\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># yum install python-pip (基于小红帽的系统)</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>Note</strong>：pip是一个简单的安装替代，是一个有极大改进的Python第三方包安装器。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><strong>下载并安装Cheat</strong></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">我们将通过Git下载‘Cheat’，确保你安装了‘git’包，如果没有最好安装一下。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1px !important;\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># apt-get install git (基于Debian的系统)</span></li><li class=\"L1\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># yum install git (基于小红帽的系统)</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">接下来，通过运行下面的命令来安装所需要的python依赖包。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1px !important;\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># pip install docopt pygments</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">现在，复制cheat的<a href=\"http://www.tecmint.com/install-git-to-create-and-share-your-own-projects-on-github-repository/\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0); transition: all 0.5s ease; text-decoration: none;\">Git库</a></p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1px !important;\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># git clone https://github.com/chrisallenlane/cheat.git</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">进入cheat目录，运行‘<strong>setup.py</strong>’（一个python脚本）。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1px !important;\"><li class=\"L0\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># cd cheat</span></li><li class=\"L1\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; border: none; line-height: 21px; font-family: Arial; background-image: url(http://images.51cto.com/images/art1105/images/0.gif); background-attachment: scroll; color: rgb(92, 92, 92); padding: 0px 3px 0px 10px !important; margin: 0px !important; list-style-position: outside !important; background-position: -498px -70px; background-repeat: no-repeat repeat;\"><span class=\"com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; font-size: 14px;\"># python setup.py install</span></li></ol></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word;\">如果安装很顺利，你就能够看到安装在系统上的cheat版本了。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 643.5px; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><ol class=\"linenums\" style=\"padding: 5px 0px 15px; margin-left: 55px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initi